      <div class="msgContentFrame"><b>FAME-QUESTS</b> *Can I Have It?* <br /> <br /> <br />I really hope we get quests some day. <br />I do like leves, but they're no replacement for quests that make you want to explore the cities and talk to people. <br />Because of the lack of quests I never get to know these NPCs wondering around cities in their hundreds containing the lines written for them. <br /> <br /> <br />Fame level in XI also made you feel like ... well helpful! And it motivated to get that fame lvl up so you could see the events of the cities of Vana'diel unfold.</div>
